{"tid":735804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大部分人聽到其他人講有臭味嘅第一個反應都係大力咁索","createTime":"2018-07-09T18:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T10:43:49.000Z","uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"866252897a8d698e68f53988facd52e1a8b204f3","tid":735804,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T18:57:39.000Z","msg":"聞到陣臭味 通常都係索多幾野確認下係咩味 依樣係好正常嘅動物特點<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲臭味 係會特別想索佢 <br />\n再癲啲 甚至自己整陣味出嚟瘋狂索<br />\n<br />\n每次剪腳甲我都會聞下腳甲屎嘅味<br />\n<br />\n白色珍珠更加唔洗講<br />\n有時用手整完頭髮 指甲位嘅頭油味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點都要聞多幾聞"},{"pid":"debb347b141a1e113986a0bd4969bbbd67ba4eff","tid":735804,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T19:11:39.000Z","msg":"唔好討論呢樣野住<br />\n有冇人聞到屁味？"},{"pid":"542426994a6ae017da70d0f55b77bb52dd2ec6ec","tid":735804,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"有時會聞吓自己對腳臭唔臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5b417252064b309a82fc2b3a02706235952045","tid":735804,"uid":60660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"黑色腳甲泥<br />\n白色珍珠<br />\n肥婆頸老泥<br />\n識食一定呢三樣"},{"pid":"208f679c09d1ca3c80c12f5548478ce93c9554b2","tid":735804,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542426994a6ae017da70d0f55b77bb52dd2ec6ec","tid":735804,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"有時會聞吓自己對腳臭唔臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"我都會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例行公事"},{"pid":"73025167894b66f6038119a14d2fa925909db2dc","tid":735804,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc5b417252064b309a82fc2b3a02706235952045"